                        </td>
                    <tr>
                </table>
            % }
            % else
            % {
                Spaghetti &mdash; forum system for developers<br>
                Current version:
                <acronym title="<%= $Spaghetti::COMMIT %>">
                    <%= $Spaghetti::VERSION %>
                </acronym><br>
                Built with <a href="http://perl.org/">Perl</a><br>
                Powered by <a href="http://lorcode.org/">LorCode</a>
            % }
            </small>
    </footer>

</div>

  </body>
</html>
